"{\"uid\": \"hngn.com-articles-262460-20240802-slovakian-swimmer-collapses-poolside-paris-olympics.htm\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A swimmer from Slovakia collapsed poolside Friday at the Paris Olympics after having an asthma attack.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.81787018231978, \"rank\": 0.2117841689323501, \"text\": \"Slovakia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamara Potocka, 21, had just competed in the qualifying heat in the women's 200-meter individual medley when she became ill,ESPNreported.\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 104, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"score\": 0.9627395456265048, \"rank\": 0.029303583550409032, \"text\": \"Tamara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\"}, {\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medical crews came to her aid and carried her away on a stretcher.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was seen wearing an oxygen mask.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Slovakian officials said Potocka had an asthma attack, and that she did not have her asthma inhaler with her to counteract shortness of breath.\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tamara has asthma,\\\" Slovakia team leader Ivana Lange said in a statement, ESPN reported.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.81787018231978, \"rank\": 0.2117841689323501, \"text\": \"Slovakia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9997220179162483, \"rank\": 0.00018458653866162617, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This whole combination of nervous and physical tension while she did not have her inhaler immediately available to use contributed to the creation of this problem.\\\"\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lange said Potocka received oxygen and her condition is being monitored.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A few minutes ago, the doctor told me that she must be monitored for several more hours,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Israeli swimmer Lea Polonsky said swimmers know their sport has risks.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"score\": 0.8832896168373351, \"rank\": 0.08103017979056909, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Polonsky\", \"score\": 0.9999968328519476, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lea Polonsky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Polonsky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Polonsky\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course that's something in the back of your mind, but we do every day push ourselves to the limit,\\\" Polonsky told theAssociated Press.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You always know something like that can happen.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not something you think about during the race, but it's always there.\\\"\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka finished seventh in the third heat and was eliminated from competition.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 HNGN, All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not reproduce without permission.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": []}]}"